17-08-02T14:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有核武洗能同你打拳頭交咩<br />\n大家都係得把囗<br />\n真係開拖 根本全世界都係輻射<br />\n死唔去仲慘過食屎</blockquote><br />\n咁整航母之後打哂飛機為乜</blockquote><br />\n對住d弱家咪用刀槍囉<br />\n但對有核武果D 一定係攬炒</blockquote><br />\n日本仔根本有原料有技術做核武，真係唔明支那拎D核彈黎打飛機做乜！"},{"pid":"b9c3bd93efe338e6c12321330d2af7505eac7e8a","tid":344810,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f67e2b00c7d948390bb5f46b28c6423dff4e4c2","tid":344810,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大日本帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本科技含量絕對追得上美國<br />\n如果唔係條約限制軍備<br />\n日本瞬間秒殺支畜啦<br />\n見住班愛國傻尻廢老日日對住習種閱兵係度打飛機真係頂唔撚順</blockquote><br />\n好似15年開始重新整返軍備啦<br />\n日本成立防衛裝備廳加速出口武器<br />\n<br />\n日本防衛省旗下的新機構－防衛裝備廳周四（10月1日）正式成立。這是基於今年6月日本國會成立的《改訂防衛省設置法》，防衛省把原來省內的研究開發部門與旗下負責自衛隊裝備、駐軍設施等的&quot;裝備設施本部&quot;合併，並在原有主打研究開發武器功能的基礎上，促進供應武器功能，尤其是促進通過與海外合作研製武器，降低防衛裝備成本來供應的統籌新機構。<br />\n防衛省技術研究本部長渡邊秀明周四上午在接受防衛大臣中谷元辭令，正式就任&quot;防衛裝備廳&quot;首任長官後，防衛省舉行了成立紀念儀式。儀式後中谷元對記者團說：&quot;今後將有效地取得裝備品並與各國從事裝備合作&quot;。<br />\n&quot;防衛裝備廳&quot;是在長官之下，設有防衛技監、長官官房、裝備政策部、計劃管理部、技術戰略部、供應管理部、供應事業部和負責研究試驗的設施機關各部，規模約1800人，其中事務人員和技術人員1400人、自衛官400人，另外配備約20名負責監督貪污腐敗的監察官，此外防衛裝備廳外還有監視體制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/10/151001_japan_military_weapons\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld%2F2015%2F10%2F151001_japan_military_weapons&d=Wei4zHdQtf64ufR8jROqkBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f46f119f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld%2F2015%2F10%2F151001_japan_military_weapons&h=27baebd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/10/151001_japan_military_weapons</a>"},{"pid":"cedf152378e2214791ad1e96194821d3908ce02c","tid":344810,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點呀，人地有新武器，就話自己夠疊馬同大隻。啫係質量贏唔到人要夠數量搭夠啦。</blockquote><br />\n質你老母量</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473bb5a82a2a471d9316709a586d1b15dab3bc73","tid":344810,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點呀，人地有新武器，就話自己夠疊馬同大隻。啫係質量贏唔到人要夠數量搭夠啦。</blockquote><br />\n質你老母量</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n質量=mass<br />\n係咪咁難明？"},{"pid":"3cc168e9f7e12a0e8189d8c67c52b06be76e1ef9","tid":344810,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"點解呢d機冇向後既武器"},{"pid":"346a76243d93dcaf57482a4017a7e5ce0aef7bd2","tid":344810,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解呢d機冇向後既武器</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本仔隻AAM-5係Thrust vectoring<br />\n係可以向後打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/AAM-5-002.jpg/300px-AAM-5-002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fe%2Fe2%2FAAM-5-002.jpg%2F300px-AAM-5-002.jpg&h=4a4745f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5eec466855a1caa70c896a80366cac6e1ef58c0","tid":344810,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T07:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}